---
description: Code review checklist
globs: 
alwaysApply: false
---
- [ ] Consistent import patterns
- [ ] Comprehensive type hints
- [ ] Proper error handling
- [ ] Google-style docstrings
- [ ] Following dataclass patterns for configs
- [ ] Appropriate logging usage
- [ ] Tests included and located in module-local `tests/` directory (integration tests belong in `integration_tests/`)
- [ ] No hardcoded values
- [ ] No placeholder logic, estimations, or "hacky" code
- [ ] Follows established naming conventions
- [ ] Full CI suite passes locally: unit/integration tests **and** Ruff linting 